node.title: Manhunt after person shot in Gisborne
node.description: The victim went to a nearby marae for assistance.
node.content: ["A person has been moderately injured in a shooting in Gisborne.\n", "Police say they were called to a report of an injured person at an address on Te Araroa Rd at about 3:15am.", "\"The victim had reportedly been shot and then gone to the nearby marae to seek assistance,\" police say.", "Officers have spoken with the victim and are making enquiries to locate the alleged offender."]
